05:12.583 --> 05:15.897
Everyone knows a Mike. Yes,
everyone does know a Mike.

05:15.921 --> 05:18.395
Actually, you're right.
I did know a Mike in college.

05:18.419 --> 05:21.067
We did this play together,
"pippin." It wasn't very good.

05:21.091 --> 05:24.435
Anyways, I never thought of him,
so you shouldn't be accusing me.

05:24.459 --> 05:26.302
I was probably
just hallucinating.

05:26.326 --> 05:28.375
Fine, fine.

05:28.399 --> 05:30.407
So... who's the guy
you're married to?

05:30.431 --> 05:32.579
Damn that nurse hisel!

05:32.603 --> 05:35.817
Or should I say, "who's the guy
you're cheating on?"

05:35.841 --> 05:37.814
Okay, yes, I did remarry my ex,

05:37.838 --> 05:40.447
