he has great health insurance.

05:40.471 --> 05:42.449
Did miss blabbermouth
tell you that, too?

05:42.473 --> 05:45.497
You... you committed insurance
fraud? Only in the legal sense.

05:45.521 --> 05:49.025
And I just didn't tell you
because I wanted to protect you.

05:49.049 --> 05:51.027
Susan... okay, you know what?

05:51.051 --> 05:53.860
You should come over to dinner
and meet Karl, and you can see

05:53.884 --> 05:56.368
