in love with anyone named Mike?

06:07.468 --> 06:10.138
Sure.

06:13.373 --> 06:15.482
Okay.

06:15.506 --> 06:17.384
Come here.

06:17.408 --> 06:20.548
I believe you.

06:21.882 --> 06:23.860
