I'd hit rock bottom.

06:33.624 --> 06:37.504
Okay, who's next?

06:37.528 --> 06:38.528
Bree.

06:40.070 --> 06:43.379
Oh! Um, I couldn't
possibly top that.

06:43.403 --> 06:44.913
Thank you, though.

06:55.185 --> 06:57.524
Hi. Before coming
to these meetings,

06:57.548 --> 07:01.568
