group that meets after us.

07:05.605 --> 07:07.804
You know, just to mess with 'em.

07:07.828 --> 07:09.576
You're awful.

07:09.600 --> 07:12.178
So... tell me, Bree,
how long have you been sober?

07:12.202 --> 07:14.941
Gosh, um...

07:14.965 --> 07:17.013
