07:36.026 --> 07:37.604
You don't say.

07:37.628 --> 07:40.106
It's true. I'm coming here
because of my son.

07:40.130 --> 07:43.109
You see, he's... he's trying
to take me to court to become

07:43.133 --> 07:46.617
an emancipated minor, and he's
planning on lying to the judge

07:46.641 --> 07:49.115
and telling him that
I am some sort of dreadful lush.

07:49.139 --> 07:51.618
