to give the impression

07:51.642 --> 07:54.626
that I have changed. But
you don't really need to change

07:54.650 --> 07:56.853
because you don't have
a problem with alcohol.

07:56.877 --> 07:59.526
Exactly.

07:59.550 --> 08:01.087
I'll tell you what...

08:01.111 --> 08:03.490
Here's my card.

08:03.514 --> 08:05.497
And if you ever dohave a problem

08:05.521 --> 08:08.464
or you just feel like talking,
give me a call, okay?

08:08.488 --> 08:10.597
I know you think
I'm kidding myself,

08:10.621 --> 08:12.138
but I'm not.

08:12.162 --> 08:14.501
I'm nothing like you people.

08:14.525 --> 08:17.565
I just don't have
a compulsive personality.

08:19.199 --> 08:20.199
Hmm.

08:26.577 --> 08:29.556
Word is out all over town
that you're unhappy at zimms,

08:29.580 --> 08:32.958
