and come to parcher & Murphy?

08:32.982 --> 08:35.597
I swear, Veronica,
you would fit in so well here.

08:35.621 --> 08:37.594
I do need
to make a change, Lynette,

08:37.618 --> 08:40.226
but the money you're offering...

08:40.250 --> 08:42.227
Yeah, it sucks,
but there are other perks...

08:42.251 --> 08:44.500
The expense account,
the corner office... I don't know.

08:44.524 --> 08:47.508
