were real jerks about that.

09:29.169 --> 09:31.648
Parcher & Murphy
is completely mother-friendly.

09:31.672 --> 09:32.819
No one would say a word.

09:32.843 --> 09:34.303
Oh!

09:36.146 --> 09:37.954
What the heck, I'm in.

09:37.978 --> 09:40.186
Yeah? Well, that's fantastic!

09:40.210 --> 09:42.759
Oh, my god,
whose kids are those?

09:45.886 --> 09:48.034
I have absolutely no idea.

09:48.058 --> 09:50.718
Let's go hammer
out the details. Okay.

09:52.292 --> 09:54.300
Mm. Ooh.

09:54.324 --> 09:56.811
These can't be
our only choices, Mr. Beale.

09:56.835 --> 09:58.775
I mean, comeon.

09:58.799 --> 10:00.807
Each girl is uglier
than the next.

10:00.831 --> 10:02.809
Look, finding a gorgeous
pregnant woman who's willing

10:02.833 --> 10:05.311
to give her baby to a couple
with a criminal record

10:05.335 --> 10:08.314
isn't exactly a walk in the park. I
don't care if it's a walk in the sewer.

10:08.338 --> 10:10.316
We are hemorrhaging money
into your bank account,

10:10.340 --> 10:13.660
and I expect to see results. You know,
Mrs. Solis,

10:13.684 --> 10:15.901
you can catch more flies
with honey than with vinegar.

10:15.925 --> 10:17.894
