I'm afraid I'm out of ideas.

10:40.871 --> 10:43.219
He's going to dump us as clients

10:43.243 --> 10:45.196
if you don't stop
being so damn picky.

10:45.220 --> 10:47.193
We're gonna
have to stare at this face

10:47.217 --> 10:48.695
for the next 18 years.

10:48.719 --> 10:51.728
I don't think now
is the time to skimp on quality.

10:51.752 --> 10:53.700
Gabrielle, Carlos...

10:53.724 --> 10:56.234
I'd like you to meet Libby.

11:03.764 --> 11:06.874
Well, now, this I can work with.

11:13.844 --> 11:15.121
