12:28.348 --> 12:30.326
Libby, you'll make a list
of your expenses,

12:30.350 --> 12:32.158
and the solises here will pay.

12:32.182 --> 12:34.861
Oh, but can't they also
buy me gifts?

12:34.885 --> 12:36.933
I knew this one girl who gave up
her baby, and she got a Harley.

12:36.957 --> 12:41.267
Well, I don't know that we can
afford a Harley, but I'm sure

12:41.291 --> 12:44.510
