to express our gratitude.

12:44.534 --> 12:46.913
Okay.

12:46.937 --> 12:47.974
Whatever.

12:47.998 --> 12:50.777
Well, my lunch break is over,

12:50.801 --> 12:53.419
so I have to get back
to the club.

12:53.443 --> 12:56.327
Till I get rid of this kid,
they got me slinging drinks.

